# Place Chinese font files here for PDF generation.
#
# Required files:
#   NotoSansTC-Regular.ttf   — body text, tables, footer
#   NotoSansTC-Bold.ttf      — headings, section titles, cover
#
# Download from Google Fonts:
#   https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Sans+TC
#
# These files are NOT committed to git (see .gitignore).
# On Streamlit Cloud, upload them manually or via git-lfs.
